            <h1 class="text-center">About Us</h1>
            <p class="text-justify">
                This institution is running since 1916 but later in 1935 this Educational Society got registered under the name Jain Shramno Pasik School, Delhi. Under Societies Registration Act XXI of 1860 vide Registration No. S/94 of 1935-1936.
                <br><br>
                Initially, the school started as a primary school in 1916, which was subsequently upgraded to middle school in 1935-36, High School in 1949, higher secondary in 1959 and it became Senior Secondary School in 1977-78. The hard work, passion and dedication of one and all helped students to Bag 1st and 2nd Position in CBSE Results in Sr. Sec. Exam 1982 and recently for the last Academic Sessions the school result is 100% both for Class-X as well as for Class-XII.
                <br><br>
                Our school is committed to providing a holistic education that nurtures the intellectual, emotional, and physical development of our students. We offer a balanced curriculum that includes a wide range of academic subjects, extracurricular activities, and sports, ensuring that each student has the opportunity to discover and develop their unique talents and interests.
                <br><br>
                Over the years, Jain Samnopasak Senior Secondary School has built a reputation for academic excellence and a supportive learning environment. Our experienced and dedicated faculty members work tirelessly to inspire and motivate students to achieve their full potential. We believe in the importance of continuous learning and encourage our students to be curious, creative, and critical thinkers. We also emphasize the importance of values and ethics, guiding our students to become responsible and compassionate members of society.
                <br><br>
                Jain Samnopasak Senior Secondary School is proud of its long-standing tradition of academic achievement and community service. We look forward to continuing our mission of providing quality education and shaping the future leaders of tomorrow.
            </p>
            
